OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FThree teenagers have been found guilty
OL,8,Ffor their roles in the rape of two
OL,9,Fgirls in a New Forest town.
OL,11,FThe trial at Southampton Crown Court
OL,12,Fheard that two girls were raped in two
OL,13,Fseparate incidents in Fordingbridge,
OL,14,FHampshire, with the first attack
OL,15,Ftaking place on November 26 2024 and
OL,16,Fthe second on January 17 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
