PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772755384
OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FA 15-year-old boy was found guilty of
OL,8,Fone charge of rape and another 15-year-
OL,9,Fold defendant was convicted of three
OL,10,Fcharges of rape in connection with the
OL,11,FNovember incident.
OL,13,FThe first defendant was also found
OL,14,Fguilty of one count of rape and the
OL,15,Fsecond defendant was convicted of
OL,16,Fthree charges of rape in connection
OL,17,Fwith the January incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
