FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772755384
OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FA third defendant, aged 14, was found
OL,8,Fguilty of two charges of rape by
OL,9,Fencouraging the second defendant in
OL,10,Fthe January incident.
OL,12,FAs the verdict against the 14-year-old
OL,13,Fwas announced by the foreman of the
OL,14,Fjury, a man in the public gallery
OL,15,Fstarted crying and said: "That's my
OL,16,Fson" before he was asked to leave the
OL,17,Fcourt by the judge.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@DO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
