PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772755384
OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FThe first defendant was also found
OL,8,Fguilty of taking indecent photos of a
OL,9,Fchild and the second defendant
OL,10,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to four
OL,11,Fcharges of taking indecent photos of a
OL,12,Fchild.
OL,14,FJodie Mittel KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,15,Ftrial that the girl in the November
OL,16,Fincident, who was 15 at the time, had
OL,17,Ffirst come into contact with the first
OL,18,Fdefendant when he sent her a friend
OL,19,Finvite on Snapchat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772755384
OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said the girl then
OL,8,Ftravelled from her home to visit him
OL,9,Fand after he had bought her a bottle
OL,10,Fof Lucozade they had been chatting in
OL,11,Fthe park.
OL,13,FThe girl agreed to go to an underpass
OL,14,Fwhere she agreed to perform sex acts
OL,15,Fon the boy, who was then 14, until
OL,16,Fthey were disturbed by passers-by, the
OL,17,Fcourt heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
