PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772755384
OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said the girl became
OL,8,F"scared and anxious" when the second
OL,9,Fdefendant, who was 14 at the time, and
OL,10,Fa third boy who is not the third
OL,11,Fdefendant, arrived and began
OL,12,F"pressuring her and they recorded her"
OL,13,Fand they were "laughing".
OL,15,FThe prosecutor said: "The word she
OL,16,Fused to describe how she was feeling
OL,17,Fwas petrified.
OL,19,F"(She) says she did agree but only
OL,20,Fbecause she didn't know what would
OL,21,Fhappen if she didn't say yes."
