OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FShe said that the boys and the girl
OL,8,Fwent back to the underpass where the
OL,9,Fgirl said she felt "cornered and
OL,10,Ftrapped" as the two defendants raped
OL,11,Fher and the second defendant filmed.
OL,13,FMs Mittel said the girl described how
OL,14,Fshe felt "numb" and added: "She says
OL,15,Fshe was shaking and saying the boys
OL,16,Fwere just laughing and recording what
OL,17,Fhappened."
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@HO]vD@JOUvD@OO]vD@\OUyD@JO]
