PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772755384
OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FMs Mittel said the incident lasted
OL,8,Faround 90 minutes, adding: "She was
OL,9,Ffeeling sick, felt like she was about
OL,10,Fto pass out, the other boys were
OL,11,Frecording whilst she sat in silence
OL,12,Ftrying her best not to cry."
OL,14,FMs Mittel said that afterwards videos
OL,15,Fof the incident had been sent around
OL,16,Fand other people made jokes about her
OL,17,Fand she received messages calling her
OL,18,Fa "slag".
OL,26,@pD@\OUtD@\O]zD@COUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
