OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FThe complainant in the January
OL,8,Fincident, who was 14 at the time, told
OL,9,Fpolice that she had been with two
OL,10,Ffriends before they went home leaving
OL,11,Fher with three other girls before the
OL,12,Fthree defendants arrived, Ms Mittel
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
