PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772755384
OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FShe said the complainant states that
OL,8,Fthe first defendant threatened her
OL,9,Fwith a knife and told her to leave her
OL,10,Fphone with an Airtag tracking device
OL,11,Fin a convenience store before making
OL,12,Fher walk to the recreation ground and
OL,13,Fa nearby field where the rape took
OL,14,Fplace.
OL,16,FMs Mittel said that CCTV footage did
OL,17,Fnot show a knife and a girl witness
OL,18,Fhad described the complainant saying
OL,19,Fthat she needed to "ditch" her phone
OL,20,Fso her mother could not track her.
OL,26,@{D@TOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
