OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772755384
OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,F"These girls were forced into sexual
OL,8,Factivity by boys who brazenly filmed
OL,9,Fthe deeply distressing incidents.
OL,11,F"After speaking with the victims in
OL,12,Fthis case and reviewing an extensive
OL,13,Ffile of evidence, it was the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service's case that these
OL,15,Fgirls were violated and could not have
OL,16,Fconsented to these terrifying
OL,17,Fencounters.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
