CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772755384
OL,3,CThree boys convicted of their roles in
OL,4,Cthe rape of two girls in New Forest
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,F"The CPS worked closely with Hampshire
OL,8,Fand Isle of Wight Constabulary to
OL,9,Fsupport the victims and other young
OL,10,Fwitnesses to give their evidence, and
OL,11,Fwe commend them for the courage they
OL,12,Fshowed throughout this trial."
